33.body: exit report? I was to find suitable templates for Sanyiko.com Here are the ones I found : drayd -- 5 star - Wordpress theme Wheat - Wordpress theme Farm - CMS template. It looks like it has a bit of php. Children Considerations: Must be wordpress based. If the website is based on a single page, it should have fast screen loading. (I have not used tools to test the speed. Just plain sight) Am starting to think that our priorities when re-making the website should be SEO-centric. Concerning the SEO thread, I found this . Single page websites versus mutiple page websites on SEO. TLDR : Concerning SEO, single page websites have advantages and disadvantages. Advantages : Your SEO wins don't get scattered across multiple pages. Domain authority of a website is mostly determined by the number of backlinks the site has been able to generate. This works to the advantage of single page websites as all the links acquired by the site point to the same URL, meaning there will always be a 1:1 ratio of links to pages. Disadvantage : You’ll have to compromise on keyword rankings. Single page websites are usually developed around one main concept. In this scenario, your ability to rank for a wide variety of keywords within the concept is quite limited. exit report?
